126
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,840
I could only vaguely remember some things.

127
00:10:30,320 --> 00:10:30,960
What do you remember?

128
00:10:31,919 --> 00:10:33,159
I remember

129
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,480
I was drinking a lot.

130
00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:37,759
I can drink a thousand cups without getting drunk.

131
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,159
I can drink a thousand cups without getting drunk.

132
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:45,360
I was just feeling bored drinking alone.

133
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:46,720
Come on, let's drink.

134
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:48,360
Come on.

135
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,039
Let's have a couple of cups.

136
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:50,799
I...

137
00:10:51,159 --> 00:10:51,799
I...

138
00:10:59,279 --> 00:10:59,960
Give me back the dart.

139
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,320
I'm going to kill Li Feiyuan

140
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:02,320
to avenge my parents.

141
00:11:03,559 --> 00:11:04,480
Don't make trouble.

142
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:06,279
First,

143
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,960
I made this dart.

144
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,039
I'm taking it back now.

145
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,000
Second,

146
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,559
