152
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,000
Wuying?

153
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,279
Is that your name?

154
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,000
What? Isn't it cool?

155
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,600
A bit pretentious.

156
