Your bed is ready.

157
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,320
Go home.

158
00:11:34,759 --> 00:11:35,480
Don't go anywhere.

159
00:11:40,799 --> 00:11:41,279
Miss Jiang.

160
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:42,679
Miss Jiang.

161
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,440
Bro.

162
00:11:54,159 --> 00:11:54,600
Wang.

163
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,919
