165
00:11:59,080 --> 00:11:59,840
She just took a sip.

166
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:00,919
Pour it.

167
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,440
Lu Duoduo.

168
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,480
Silly dog.

169
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,120
Last time I got drunk,

170
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,559
