184
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,480
Come back!

185
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:35,320
Come back!

186
00:13:36,840 --> 00:13:37,720
How many times have I told you?

187
00:13:37,879 --> 00:13:38,840
Don't trust strangers.

188
00:13:39,399 --> 00:13:40,360
What if he takes you away?

189
00:13:40,639 --> 00:13:42,120
That brother is very pretty.

190
00:13:42,279 --> 00:13:43,279
He doesn't look like a bad person.

191
00:13:43,679 --> 00:13:44,519
Don't throw things around.

192
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,000
The prettier they look,

193
00:13:47,159 --> 00:13:48,080
the more deceptive they are.

194
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,039
Don't you know that about poisonous mushrooms?

195
00:13:51,279 --> 00:13:53,639
Humans are indeed suspicious and narcissistic.

196
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,879
Good intentions are misunderstood

197
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,519
