210
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:26,360
and saved me.

211
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,440
Hypocrite!

212
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,840
Later, she hid me in her mansion,

213
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,279
bringing me food every day.

214
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:36,039
Even when her father found out,

215
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,000
she went on a hunger strike to protest,

216
00:14:38,159 --> 00:14:39,360
just to keep me alive.

217
00:14:43,919 --> 00:14:44,840
Without her,

218
00:14:45,519 --> 00:14:47,399
I would have died in the snow.

219
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,480
What you see now

220
00:14:51,799 --> 00:14:52,600
doesn't exist.

221
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,399
So what?

222
00:14:55,159 --> 00:14:55,799
She's a Li.

223
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,559
She's an enemy.

224
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:00,759
And you were abandoned in the end.

225
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:04,879
For me,

226
00:15:05,399 --> 00:15:06,399
is Li Feiyuan more of a benefactor

227
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,039
or an enemy?

228
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:09,320
A Che,

229
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:12,120
